  <title>Boaz (Pillar)</title>
  <body>
<p class="h1">BOAZ (P<span class="lc">illar</span>)</p>
<p class="fl">Name (meaning “strength”) given to one of the two pillars erected in front of King Solomon’s temple (<a href="?bref=1Kgs.7.21">1 Kgs 7:21</a>; <a href="?bref=2Chr.3.17">2 Chr 3:17</a>). <span class="ital">See</span> <a href="?item=Temple_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Temple</a>; <a href="?item=JachinandBoaz_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Jachin and Boaz</a>.</p>
